      <title>Nippon Steel Slumps在70亿美元的美国钢铁投资报告中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/nippon-steel-slumps-on-report-of-7-billion-us-steel-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Nippon Steel Corp.周五在一份报告中股价下跌，该​​报告称，该公司正在考虑投资多达70亿美元以升级美国钢铁公司，如果该公司因其拟议的141亿美元收购而赢得了批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/nippon-steel-slumps-on-report-of-7-billion-us-steel-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 00:47:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
